0
(a+b+c)^{2}=a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}+2ab+2ac+2bc=a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}+2abc\big(\frac{1}{c}+\frac{1}{b}+\frac{1}{a}\big)=a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}
\frac{1}{a}+\frac{1}{b}+\frac{1}{c}=0
